figsize = (12,12)

for s in sites.keys():
    G = ox.graph_from_point(sites[s][0], dist=sites[s][1], dist_type='network', network_type="all")

    edges = []
    for u, v, key, data in G.edges(keys=True, data=True):
        edge = dict(
            u=u,
            v=v,
            key=key
        )
        edge.update(data)
        edges.append(edge)
    df = pd.DataFrame.from_records(edges)
    if 'width' in df.columns:
        df['width'] = df.width.apply(lambda l: l if isinstance(l,list) or l !='narrow' else '0.5')
    else:
        df['width'] = df.lanes.apply(lambda l: l if isinstance(l,list) or l !='narrow' else '0.5')
    df['width'] = df['width'].apply(lambda l: max(map(float,l)) if isinstance(l,list) else float(l))
    df['lanes'] = df['lanes'].apply(lambda l: max(map(float,l)) if isinstance(l,list) else float(l))
    df['maxspeed'] = df['maxspeed'].apply(
        lambda s: float(
            ''.join([
                c for c in s if c.isdigit()
            ])) 
        if isinstance(s,str) else None)
    df['display_width'] = df[['width','lanes']].sum(axis=1).fillna(1.0)+1

    fig, ax = ox.plot_graph(G, figsize=figsize, node_size=32,bgcolor='black',
                        edge_linewidth=df['display_width'].values, edge_color='w', 
                        show=False, close=False)
    ax.scatter(*reversed(sites[s][0]), c='#0072BC', s=512, marker = 'v')
    fig.savefig(f'{s}.svg')
    fig.savefig(f'{s}.png')
